---
title: Feta Bison Burgers with Greek Village Salad
description: The delicious, dribble-down-your-chin simplicity of the noble burger can be re-invented time and time again to create the best dinnertime results. For this incarnation, we've put a Greek-inspired twist on it with feta cheese and tomato-cucumber salad!
